54:46.017 --> 54:48.350
But you gotta
           make it pay.

55:05.036 --> 55:06.535
<i> Bartley...</i>

55:06.537 --> 55:10.506
<i> he need to put</i>
  <i> his music in that machine.</i>

55:10.508 --> 55:12.274
