<i> ¶ My only sin is in my skin</i>

57:55.673 --> 57:57.272
<i> ¶ What did I do, babe</i>

57:57.274 --> 57:58.207
Bartley!

57:58.209 --> 58:01.910
<i> ¶ To be so black and blue?</i>

58:02.847 --> 58:04.213
Bartley!

