[SOMBER MUSIC PLAYING]

01:04:56.360 --> 01:04:58.093
[INMATES WAILING]

01:05:00.964 --> 01:05:04.199
Playing with George Baquet,
          good business.

01:05:08.872 --> 01:05:10.572
[WATER DRIPPING]

