[CREAKS SHUT]

01:06:26.984 --> 01:06:29.084
[HEAVY BREATHING]

01:06:41.431 --> 01:06:43.498
[NORA GRUNTING]

01:06:43.967 --> 01:06:46.501
[SCREAMING]

01:06:49.006 --> 01:06:50.638
[GROANING]

01:06:52.676 --> 01:06:54.442
[GRUNTING]

01:06:54.444 --> 01:06:56.511
[JAZZ MUSIC PLAYING]

01:07:04.021 --> 01:07:05.286
[SCREAMING]

01:07:16.633 --> 01:07:19.334
[CROWD CHEERING]

01:07:19.336 --> 01:07:22.103
BOLDEN: <i> My daddy gave me</i>
    <i> the power of my lungs.</i>

01:07:22.105 --> 01:07:24.439
<i> That's how I play like I do.</i>

01:07:25.675 --> 01:07:26.608
[SCREAMING]

01:07:27.611 --> 01:07:29.210
[CROWD SHOUTING]

01:07:38.955 --> 01:07:41.322
[CROWD SHOUTING]

01:07:42.492 --> 01:07:43.425
[MAN COUGHING]

01:07:43.427 --> 01:07:44.492
[SCREAMING]

