[GROWLS]

01:11:48.138 --> 01:11:49.671
[PLAYING OFF TUNE]

01:11:59.049 --> 01:12:00.481
Come on.

01:12:00.483 --> 01:12:01.949
Get on out of here.

01:12:03.553 --> 01:12:05.720
Motherfucker!
         Get off of me!

01:12:05.722 --> 01:12:07.455
[BOLDEN SHOUTING]

01:12:09.359 --> 01:12:11.326
Cornish, where's Warner?

01:12:15.932 --> 01:12:18.132
BOLDEN: <i> You made</i>
     <i> all your crowd crazy,</i>
         <i> caused a riot.</i>

