        your goddamn horn.

01:12:20.103 --> 01:12:22.937
That's what
     the motherfuckers want.
      That's what you'll do.

01:12:28.178 --> 01:12:29.877
[HISSING]

01:12:30.714 --> 01:12:32.513
[SCREAMING]

01:12:34.117 --> 01:12:35.850
What we gonna do here?

01:12:43.760 --> 01:12:45.259
MAN: <i> What's wrong</i>
         <i> with the man?</i>

01:12:45.261 --> 01:12:46.894
CORNISH: <i> He gone</i>
        <i> lost his mind.</i>

01:12:47.464 --> 01:12:48.996
Look, he ain't no Bolden,

